==Trivia==
*Named after [[wikipedia:Tenryū_River|Tenryu River]] in Shizuoka Prefecture; her name literally means "Heavenly Dragon".
**A Training Support Ship, JS Tenryu (ATS-4203) is in service with the modern JMSDF.
*Despite being launched in 1918, she was capable of sinking the [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/USS_Quincy_(CA-39) USS Quincy] with two torpedoes, an impressive feat considering that the [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/New_Orleans-class_cruiser New Orleans-class] heavy cruisers were at least 16 years newer than herself.
*Her left eyepatch is a reference to one of her searchlight that got damaged during the Solomon Islands Campaign.
*Sunk by [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/USS_Albacore_(SS-218) USS ''Albacore'' (SS-218)] 18 December 1942, off [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Madang Madang], New Guinea.
* In the movie, Tenryuu's sword is not a just a mere decoration; she used it to deflect incoming shells.

